name: COHMAP chron 4
notes: 1 C-14 date used (2.8k), 3 C-14 dates deleted (2.4,6.3,16.9k) and 2 stratigraphic dates inserted from Delorme. 5.5k for Picea rise and 6.2k for Alnus decline from 60%. Age bounds for application of the model: top = 0; bottom = 6500.
